"AI Translator & Editor"

Translate/Edit your PPT or any document in multiple languages including Arabic within a minute.

Here are the steps:

1- Go to www.auxi.ai/trial

2- Install the auxi on your Windows and log in using your account

3- Open your presentation or document

4- Type translate into "smart bar" OR Use for editing

5- Choose the "language" for translation and it will flip the content into the desired language

